FTP - % of Bachelor's degree conferred to women (1970 - 2011) in the USÂ¶

Summary:

  • Women dominated majors (above 50%):
    • Health Professions, Public Administration, Education, Foreign Languages and English - best from 1970 to today
    • Psycology and Art and Performance - between 40% and 60% by 1970 and above 60% today
    • Communications and Journalism and Biology - slightly above 20% in 1970, above 50% today

fte_20.set_xlim(left = 1969, right = 2011)

fte_above_20 = women_majors.plot(x = 'Year', y = above_20.index, figsize = (12,8), color = colours, legend = False)

fte_above_20.tick_params(axis = 'both', which = 'major', labelsize = 18)

fte_above_20.xaxis.label.set_visible(False)
